If you use an instance of <%= vars.ops_manager %> that you configured previously to install other runtimes, perform the following steps before you install <%= vars.product_short %>:

1. Navigate to Ops Manager.
1. Open the **Director Config** pane.
1. Select the **Enable Post Deploy Scripts** check box.
1. Click the **Installation Dashboard** link to return to the Installation Dashboard.
1. Click **Review Pending Changes**. Select all products you intend to deploy and review the changes. For more information, see [Reviewing Pending Product Changes](https://docs.vmware.com/en/VMware-Tanzu-Operations-Manager/3.0/vmware-tanzu-ops-manager/install-review-pending-changes.html).
1. Click **Apply Changes**.
